492,"uid":84267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:28:11.000Z","msg":"皮已正"},{"pid":"db8da3e733eb8b2c7e4f716acc54414a7aa7aa87","tid":133492,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a7b67154efac130f0f2e44e48ae36f22e54ade","tid":133492,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:33:19.000Z","msg":"遲d 可能又黎多次03咁差呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有多次負碌嘅機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n誠哥都話差過沙士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家買到樓仲要供嘅應該都會變負資產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd6e56313c5d84bdaa4a09751bc47ceb058d64d","tid":133492,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:35:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n2000\t 25 790<br />\n2001\t 26 262<br />\n2002\t 34 035<br />\n2003\t 26 397<br />\n2004\t 26 036<br />\n2005\t 17 321<br />\n2006\t 16 579<br />\n2007\t 10 471<br />\n2008\t 8 776<br />\n2009\t 7 157<br />\n2010\t 13 405<br />\n2011\t 9 449<br />\n2012\t 10 149<br />\n2013\t 8 254<br />\n2014\t 15 719<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2015\t 11 280<br />\n2016\t 14 595</span><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n差餉物業估價署<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rvd.gov.hk/doc/en/statistics/private_domestic.xls\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rvd.gov.hk%2Fdoc%2Fen%2Fstatistics%2Fprivate_domestic.xls&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=1438958b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rvd.gov.hk/doc/en/statistics/private_domestic.xls</a></blockquote><br />\n梁振英又話自己加左幾多幾多供應<br />\n但我睇唔出分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a2fe4664533b0a1a9ee75a0f366b9da881da7d7","tid":133492,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"