i\" /> <br />\n唯一解釋係下任政府有樓起"},{"pid":"cea47caaa305fd6e38586d66bf51420760f20ae5","tid":133492,"uid":6590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:41:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再睇埋公屋個數<br />\n<br />\n2006/07 \t\t7 192<br />\n2007/08 \t\t13 726<br />\n2008/09 \t\t19 050<br />\n2009/10 \t\t15 389<br />\n2010/11 \t\t13 672<br />\n2011/12 \t\t11 186<br />\n2012/13 \t\t13 114<br />\n2013/14 \t\t14 057<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2014/15 \t\t9 938<br />\n2015/16 \t  \t14 264</span><br />\n<br />\n唔明粱振英話佢有做野係咩意思</blockquote><br />\n老虎蟹都話自己有做啦<br />\n港豬鬼識揀依d野黎睇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7145d91fb3e3d98f937f8bbf84ef63ed593ed6d","tid":133492,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n人口多至700萬起屋反而越少，貪曾重話想一千萬人口，根本<span style=\"color: red;\">蓄謀奴役港人已久</span></blockquote><br />\n貪曾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"269a41591f3ca3e23dc3a34b0e2ab48627480db1","tid":133492,"uid":2545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:46:29.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢個世界就係有太多人識少少扮代表<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最撚憎"},{"pid":"40e4fe7fdb31db8962b3041bde5a3778350360f9","tid":133492,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:53:17.000Z","msg":"順帶講下工程成本(同外勞)<br />\n<br />\n有d building cost index,labour index可以參考<br />\n不過暫時search唔到,用第二個index頂住先<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.censtatd.gov.hk/fd.jsp?file=B10600072016MM11B0100.pdf&amp;product_id=B1060007&amp;lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Ffd.jsp%3Ffile%3DB10600072016MM11B0100.pdf%26product_id%3DB1060007%26lang%3D2&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=170a1186\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.censtatd.gov.hk/fd.jsp?file=B10600072016MM11B0100.pdf&amp;product_id=B1060007&amp;lang=2</a><br />\n<br />\n公營建築工程的工資及材料成本指數  (2003年4月 = 100)<br />\n<br />\nComposite labour wages for civil engineering contracts 158.1<br />\nComposite labour wages for building contracts 152.9<br />\n<br />\n對比起03年升左5成,對樓價幾大影響,應唔應該輸入外勞,見人見智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69284b9b9f2c229118d77d547ca0356bae74601f","tid":133492,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再睇埋公屋個數<br />\n<br />\n2006/07 \t\t7 192<br />\n2007/08 \t\t13 726<br />\n2008/09 \t\t19 050<br />\n2009/10 \t\t15 389<br />\n2010/11 \t\t13 672<br />\n2011/12 \t\t11 186<br />\n2012/13 \t\t13 114<br />\n2013/14 \t\t14 057<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2014/15 \t\t9 938<br />\n2015/16 \t  \t14 264</span><br />\n<br />\n唔明粱振英話佢有做野係咩意思</blockquote><br />\nsource: 房屋委員會"},{"pid":"80951269845e3b419e41fa1361a590f2a273a5f9","tid":133492,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"所以曾任權坐監好合理."},{"pid":"e7f150fc1f6e1533c4833bc2c688b3d3b43c384b","tid":133492,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:00:57.000Z","msg":"好多廢老中坑都唔認清個社會同時代發展成點<br />\n更加唔講一部分親中建制"},{"pid":"3fb3941a0f02817a2063e53bbfbc5e457bf5cc0e","tid":133492,"uid":61974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T17:02:47.000Z","msg":"對於呢種早已植根在心底既歪念係唔能夠透過直言更正 <br />\n因為呢班人只會堅守自己信念無視你既觀點"},{"pid":"38a6d3eca34bb6e689d2861ba094119a622a4259","tid":133492,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":